#: src/polkitmateauthenticationdialog.c:709
msgid ""
"An application is attempting to perform an action that requires privileges. "
"Authentication as one of the users below is required to perform this action."
msgstr ""
"Een Anwennen will eene Aktioon dörföhren, wat verhoogte Rechten bruukt. Du "
"muttst di as een vun de unnernstahn Brukers utwiesen, um deese Aktioon "
"dörtoföhren."

#: src/polkitmateauthenticationdialog.c:717
msgid ""
"An application is attempting to perform an action that requires privileges. "
"Authentication is required to perform this action."
msgstr ""
"Een Anwennen will eene Aktioon dörföhren, wat verhoogte Rechten bruukt. Du "
"muttst di utwiesen, um deese Aktioon dörtoföhren."

#: src/polkitmateauthenticationdialog.c:723
msgid ""
"An application is attempting to perform an action that requires privileges. "
"Authentication as the super user is required to perform this action."
msgstr ""
"Een Anwennen will eene Aktioon dörföhren, wat verhoogte Rechten bruukt. Du "
"muttst di as de Superbruker utwiesen, um deese Aktioon dörtoföhren."

